Class SshProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.parallec.core.commander.workflow.ssh.SshProvider

  • public class SshProvider
extends java.lang.Object
    based on Jsch. tested with real VM with Key/password cases. Run ssh. This is a basic one that works with password. If needed we may replace this SshProvider after defining an interface.
    Author:
    Yuanteng (Jeff) Pei
